title: Looking for a Team
body:
Hi, I'm Istezz and I'm looking for a team that consists of silver 1 + players.  I main jungle but can excel in basically everything else with top being my worst lane. I would like to join a team that wants to have fun but also be serious at the same time.

Add me in-game or leave your names down below and we can talk 

NOTE: THIS IS NOT ME MAKING A TEAM, THIS IS ME LOOKING FOR A TEAM

IGN: Istezz
Age: 17 (18 this may)
Season 4 Rank: Silver 1 (99lp)
Season 5 Rank: Gold 3 (0lp)
Preferred Lane: Jungle
Other lanes I excel in: Mid, Adc and Support
Preferred Voice Communication: Teamspeak or Skype

replies.body: Dammit Istezz why you no ask me :P
If anyone added me you may need to retry
